					<description><![CDATA[<p>Subtle Medical Secures New Capital for Global Expansion Subtle Medical has secured $33 million in growth capital to address these challenges. The financing was anchored by a Series C round</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://ventureburn.com/subtle-medical-secures-33-million-expand-ai-imaging/" data-wpel-link="internal">Subtle Medical Secures $33 Million to Expand AI Medical Imaging Platform</a> appeared first on <a href="https://ventureburn.com" data-wpel-link="internal">Ventureburn</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2><b>Subtle Medical Secures New Capital for Global Expansion</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Subtle Medical has secured $33 million in growth capital to address these challenges. The financing was anchored by a Series C round led by Morgan Stanley Expansion Capital. Additional participation came from Shinhan Venture Investment and existing investors including Fusion Fund, EnvisionX, BRV, and Samsung Ventures.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The medical imaging sector continues to face growing pressure from rising patient demand. Many healthcare providers struggle with limited scanner capacity. Long waiting times remain a challenge in many regions.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The latest raise brings the company’s total funding to $86 million. The new capital will support product development.And further expedite market commercialization into global markets. Subtle Medical plans to enhance its vendor-neutral imaging platform. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The company specializes in providing healthcare providers with the ability to improve their imaging efficiencies without the need to replace existing hardware. This investment indicates the ongoing faith in the capabilities of AI to support various applications within healthcare. The operational efficiency is quickly becoming seen as a huge opportunity by investors.</span></p>
<h2><b>AI Imaging Technology Addresses Healthcare Bottlenecks</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The importance of medical imaging is an indispensable component of modern healthcare; although some imaging techniques can consume a long time and large amount of resources, which consequently can lead to delays on both patients and providers side. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Subtle Medical has invented software to enhance image quality using artificial intelligence.The technology also shortens scanning times on existing imaging equipment. This approach helps hospitals increase throughput without making costly infrastructure investments.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The company’s solutions support reductions of up to 80 percent in scan duration. Faster examinations can improve patient comfort. They can also reduce scheduling backlogs across healthcare systems.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Subtle Medical’s products are already deployed on more than 1,300 scanners worldwide. The customer base includes hospitals, imaging centres, and academic medical institutions. Healthcare organisations using the platform have reported improvements in operational efficiency. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">They have also experienced better patient experiences through shorter examination times. The company’s flagship products include SubtleHD for MRI imaging and SubtlePET for positron emission </span><a href="https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/materials-science/tomography" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener external noreferrer" data-wpel-link="external"><span style="font-weight: 400">tomography</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400">. These tools are designed to improve workflow efficiency while maintaining diagnostic quality.</span></p>
<h2><b>Leadership Changes Support Commercial Growth</b></h2>
<div id="attachment_202206" style="width: 1322px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-202206" class="size-full wp-image-202206" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/create-a-futuristic-neon-lit-poster-elem_CJx4NUNaXPyurbuobnqIQQ_KDPSay0MTaalIJu1Wics_w.png" alt="Healthcare leadership with AI imaging systems and global medical technology network." width="1312" height="736" /><p id="caption-attachment-202206" class="wp-caption-text">Subtle Medical strengthens leadership to drive global AI imaging expansion. Source: Created by Ventureburn</p></div>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">In addition to the funding announcement Subtle Medical has also added to their team. They announced that Ohad Arazi will be their new Chief Executive Officer. Arazi has a background in medical imaging having held many positions in healthcare technology including leadership at Change Healthcare, Zebra Medical Vision, and Clarius Mobile Health. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">He also has knowledge in both enterprise software and medical imaging technologies. According to Arazi the company is no longer operating a one product-at-a-time business model and instead thinks they are creating a layered AI infrastructure over the imaging operations. Former Chief Executive Officer Enhao Gong will be changing his title to Chief Science Officer. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">He will continue leading the company’s scientific direction. He will also support strategic partnerships and operations in China. The leadership changes are designed to support the company’s next phase of commercial expansion. Management believes stronger global execution will help increase adoption among hospitals and healthcare networks.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The company also continues to receive recognition across the healthcare technology sector. Its solutions have earned multiple industry awards and regulatory clearances. These achievements strengthen its position within the growing medical imaging market.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">More News: <a href="https://ventureburn.com/ilant-health-raises-15-million-obesity-care/" data-wpel-link="internal">Ilant Health Raises $15 Million to Expand Value-Based Obesity Care</a></span></p>
<h2><b>Unified Imaging Platform Drives Future Strategy</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">A central part of Subtle Medical’s growth strategy is its AI Imaging Hub. The platform provides healthcare systems with a unified management layer across different imaging devices. Many providers currently operate equipment from multiple manufacturers. Managing separate software solutions can increase complexity. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Subtle Medical aims to simplify this process through a single platform. The Imaging Hub supports MRI, PET, and CT environments. Healthcare organisations can standardise imaging performance across their networks. This helps improve consistency and operational efficiency.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Unlike manufacturer-specific software, the platform operates independently of equipment brands. This flexibility allows providers to scale artificial intelligence adoption more easily. Subtle Medical is also investing in new imaging technologies.  One area of focus involves reducing gadolinium contrast usage during MRI examinations. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">It is predicted that the company&#8217;s SubtleGAD technology could drastically reduce contrast dosages while retaining image quality. The progress made within this area further solidifies trends seen throughout healthcare. With the growing need for provider efficiency as well as high quality patient outcomes.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Experts forecast that over the coming years, AI will have an increasing part in the overall radiologic work-stream. Those solutions that can improve efficiency and patient care while minimizing capital expense to providers may be increasingly popular. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The company states that its platform is currently being used by providers to improve scanner utilization and reduce delays in scanning that could affect patient care.  These factors remain key as the healthcare systems navigate an increase in volume of imaging studies performed. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">With the additional investment, Subtle Medical believes it has the resources to accelerate innovation for its products. In addition to expanding its sales to new geographic areas and market segments. In terms of a growing customer base and strengthened management team. The company appears poised for the next steps in the development of its AI imaging platform.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">To stay updated on crypto venture capital funding and market trends, visit our </span><a href="https://ventureburn.com/category/news/venture-capital/" data-wpel-link="internal"><span style="font-weight: 400">venture capital news section</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400"> for more insights.</span></p>
